headline: ePlus Named Digital Realty's 2024 Rising Star Partner of the Year
summary: ePlus inc. (NASDAQ NGS: PLUS – news) today announced that it has been recognized as Digital Realty's 2024 Rising Star Partner of the Year. ePlus was presented with the award in acknowledgement of its commitment to partnership and demonstrated AI innovation expertise that helps customers achieve desired AI-related business outcomes.

headline: 18 US REITs Forecast To Boost Dividends In Q3 2025
summary: Eighteen publicly traded US real estate investment trusts are expected to raise dividend payouts in the third quarter, according to S&P Global Market Intelligence forecasts.
